pageProduct.name: Thompson's One-A-Day Organic Olive Leaf 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's One-A-day Organic Olive Leaf 5000mg is traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to relieve mild fever.

Thompson's One-A-Day Organic Olive Leaf is formulated for convenience with a One-A-Day dose. Olive Leaf is used Traditionally in Western herbal medicine to relieve mild fever and reduce body temperature. It can also be used to/as:
- An antioxidant; Reduce free radicals formed in the body and decrease their damage to body cells.
- Maintain general health & wellbeing.

Suitable For: Vegetarian/Vegan friendly

Size: 60 Capsules

Oil-Free?: Yes

KEY FEATURES

• antioxidant; Reduce free radicals formed in the body and decrease their damage to body cells
• Maintains general health & wellbeing

Warnings

If symptoms persist, talk to your healthcare professional. Not to be used in children under 5 years. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken.

CAUTION

Keep out of reach of children.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Active ingredients per capsule:
Olea europaea (Olive) ext. 500mg
derived from dry leaf 5g (5000mg)
std. to contain Oleuropein 100mg

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Egg| Fish| Gluten| Lactose| Nuts| Sesame Seeds

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Remove cap. Recycle glass bottle

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
